  "body": "Besu validates (see TimestampValidationRuleTest) that blocks are no more than 15s into the future, as per https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1482\n\ngeth has this validation rule for ethash https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/4e474c74dc2ac1d26b339c32064d0bac98775e77/consensus/ethash/consensus.go#L45\n\nbut no longer in beacon consensus https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/consensus/beacon/consensus.go#L226\n\nThink we can remove this validation rule from mainnet PoS consensus",
